    "description": "<strong>Defeat enemies as they rush towards you, upgrade your weapons to prepare for more powerful enemies!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls</strong></h2>The player can switch weapons with the number 1 and number 2 keys.<br>The player can run with the left shift key and jump with the space key.<br>Melee attacks do not exist.<br>The controls are the same as most FPS games, but if you're new to the game, be sure to check the skill keys in the settings window.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Victory Conditions</strong></h2>Battles are fought in waves.<br>A wave begins with an enemy spawning in one of the four regions,<br>enemies always travel to the player's location.<br>The wave ends when all enemies are defeated, and the next wave begins after a certain amount of time.<br><br>The player wins if they survive 30 waves.<br>Every 10 waves, a boss appears. Be prepared to battle bosses with powerful patterned attacks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Resources</strong></h2>When capturing an enemy, the player gains a certain amount of experience. When maximizing experience, players gain skill points and recover a certain amount of HP.<br><br>In addition, at the beginning of each wave, a supply crate spawns in the sky.<br>Attacking and destroying supply crates will give you a large amount of skill points and ammo.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skills</strong></h2>Pressing the F1(default) key opens the Skills window.<br>In the Skills window, you can enhance your player's stats or gain skills that are useful against enemies.<br>You can select up to four types of skills, and for active skills, you can freely set a hotkey for the skill to use in the Skills window.",
